metadata.name: The Crypto Bro Brings the Bull Back
metadata.description:
A crypto Bro with sharpened claws  
Bringing back the Bull market with a roar  
His trades swift and sharp as a knife  
Making profits and causing others strife

The market rises with his every move  
As he deftly navigates through  
The highs and lows, the twists and turns  
With a bullish fervor that swiftly burns

The Bull seems back, and the Bro is here  
Riding the wave, without sorrows and fear  
But danger lurks, as the market turns  
And the Bear reveals its sharpened claws

The Bro must navigate with skill and grace  
To avoid the pitfalls of this deadly race  
But fear not, dear Bro, you are strong  
And the Bull that carries you is just as fierce

Together you'll weather the storm and rise  
Victorious over the Bear's dark skies  
And though the Bear may howl and growl  
You'll emerge triumphant, a legend to behold.
